@description.name: @description
@description
@description.body:
Returns all relevant properties of the cell:
  • classes (String): Space separated class names
  • style (String): CSS styles
  • attributes (String): Space separated attributes
  • content (String): HTML fragment of the innerHTML of the cell
  • insets (Array): insets (padding + border) of the cell as two-dimensional array.

@param.name: @param
@param.body: data {var} Data needed for the cell to render.
@param.description: Data needed for the cell to render.

@param.name: @param
@param.body: states {Map} The states set on the cell (e.g. selected, focused, editable).
@param.description: The states set on the cell (e.g. selected, focused, editable).
